metadata.name: Sandalfon
metadata.description:
A token of gratitude minted for all of those who decided to support my art journey into the NFT space on Ethereum and found value in my art. A sincere thank you! 

Inspired by classical realistic paintings and Christian mythology. Older depictions of angels as more unsettling and powerful celestial beings, in particular. 
An AI output was used to generate the initial idea, which was composited and overpainted in Photoshop to produce the final digital painting. 

Created by Dariusz Kieliszek.
